Author: onthewaydownnn
Text: F   Ah god I feel you so hard. I don’t just binge for a day, I go on benders where I’ll binge for weeks at a time. And that first day without a binge is the FUUUUCKING WORST. Like your whole body is depriving itself from oxygen or something.   I’m so sorry that’s where you’re at right now. It’s not easy to exit that cycle but it is possible. Love you <3
